Persim-Pervasive Human Activity Simulator
Dataset/Project Repository

Persim Project
Mobile and Pervasive Computing Lab
University of Florida
http://www.icta.ufl.edu/projects_persim.htm
persim.info@gmail.com

Updated: Mar.30.2011

This is a repository for human activity. In this repository, there are datasets
and project files used for Persim human activity simulator which is developed
by Mobile and Pervasive Computing Lab at University of Florida. 
The datasets include datasets collected in real world and datasets generated by 
Persim. The datasets are formed in Standard Dataset Discription Language(SDDL) 
format for sharing with all the research groups. The project files are loaded 
into Persim to simulate activities. 
For more information, please check Persim project homepage and papers.